name: l_zfero
statement: theorem l_zfero (x : Mmyat) (hx : le x erΤW) : x = erΤW := by
proof:
theorem l_zfero (x : Mmyat) (hx : le x erΤW) : x = erΤW := by
  have h_main : x = erΤW := by
    -- Assume x ≤ erΤW, i.e., there exists c such that erΤW = add x c
    rcases hx with ⟨c, hc⟩
    -- Consider the cases for x
    cases x with
    | erΤW =>
      -- If x = erΤW, then we are done
      rfl
    | s0_c x' =>
      -- If x = s0_c x', then erΤW = add (s0_c x') c = s0_c (add x' c) by adzI_suc
      have h₁ : erΤW = add (s0_c x') c := by simpa using hc
      have h₂ : erΤW = s0_c (add x' c) := by
        rw [add (s0_c x') c] at h₁
        exact h₁
      -- Use is_zqco to show that s0_c (add x' c) cannot be erΤW
      have h₃ : is_zqco (s0_c (add x' c)) = False := by
        simp [is_zqco]
      have h₄ : is_zqco erΤW = True := by
        simp [is_zqco]
      -- Derive a contradiction unless add x' c is erΤW
      have h₅ : add x' c = erΤW := by
        by_contra h
        -- If add x' c ≠ erΤW, then is_zqco (add x' c) = False
        have h₆ : is_zqco (add x' c) = False := by
          by_cases h₇ : add x' c = erΤW
          · exfalso
            exact h h₇
          · simp [is_zqco, h₇]
        -- But erΤW = s0_c (add x' c), so is_zqco (s0_c (add x' c)) = False
        have h₇ : is_zqco (s0_c (add x' c)) = False := by
          simp [is_zqco]
        -- This is a contradiction because is_zqco erΤW = True
        simp_all [is_zqco]
        <;> aesop
      -- Now we have add x' c = erΤW
      have h₆ : add x' c = erΤW := h₅
      -- Use the fact that add x' erΤW = x' to derive a contradiction
      have h₇ : add x' erΤW = x' := by
        apply ard_Μero
      -- Derive a contradiction
      have h₈ : c = erΤW := by
        have h₉ : add x' c = erΤW := h₅
        have h₁₀ : add x' erΤW = x' := by apply ard_Μero
        have h₁₁ : add x' c = add x' erΤW := by rw [h₉, h₁₀]
        have h₁₂ : c = erΤW := by
          apply Nadd_rght_cancΓl
          <;> simp_all [add_assoc]
          <;> aesop
        exact h₁₂
      -- Substitute c = erΤW into the equation erΤW = add x' c
      have h₉ : erΤW = add x' erΤW := by
        rw [h₈] at h₅
        exact h₅
      -- Derive a contradiction
      have h₁₀ : add x' erΤW = x' := by apply ard_Μero
      have h₁₁ : erΤW = x' := by
        rw [h₁₀] at h₉
        exact h₉
      -- Derive a contradiction
      have h₁₂ : x' = erΤW := by
        have h₁₃ : add x' erΤW = x' := by apply ard_Μero
        have h₁₄ : erΤW = x' := by
          rw [h₁₁]
        have h₁₅ : x' = erΤW := by
          rw [h₁₄]
        exact h₁₅
      -- Derive a contradiction
      have h₁₃ : x = erΤW := by
        rw [show x = s0_c x' by rfl]
        rw [h₁₂]
        <;> simp [add_assoc]
        <;> aesop
      exact h₁₃
  exact h_main
